text.0:
A widely shared post on social media cherry-picks the data on flu and pneumonia deaths.

This makes the fall in 2020 look more extreme than it really is.

https://t.co/60wZaZxbqf
text.1:
It’s been claimed on Facebook that suicide deaths have been higher than coronavirus deaths in the last two months.

There is no evidence for this. We don’t know how many suicides have happened yet.

https://t.co/LCDKV8bt7B

Today I'm thrilled to publish our 1st discussion paper & announce some of the amazing people whose expertise we have been drawing on. A thread:down_arrow_selector:
